pravacanam api | 

	samastavedasiddhānāṃ kṛtānām īśvarādibhiḥ |
	bauddhānāṃ tantramantrāṇāṃ viśeṣaḥ śunyatāṃ prati ||

itthaṃ praviṣṭasyedānīṃ sarvābhiniveśatyāgam āha—tyajetyādi | subodham ||

<commentary>catuḥkoṭirahitatā cety āha—nāsata ityādi | subodham ||</commentary>

parāgamasāmyam uktvā svāgamavirodham āha—kiṃ cetyādi | iha hi madhyamakādivicārito 'rtho mantranaye phalena devatāyogena khyāpyate |
